下面给你一个 完整 Python 示例（最常见写法）。
1 触发 GitLab Pipeline（带变量）
GitLab API：

POST /projects/:id/pipeline
Python 示例：
Python
import requests

GITLAB_URL = "https://gitlab.com"
PROJECT_ID = "123456"
TOKEN = "your_token"

url = f"{GITLAB_URL}/api/v4/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/pipeline"

payload = {
    "ref": "main",
    "variables": [
        {"key": "TEST_DURATION", "value": "5"},
        {"key": "ENV", "value": "staging"}
    ]
}

headers = {
    "PRIVATE-TOKEN": TOKEN
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=payload)

data = response.json()

pipeline_id = data["id"]

print("Pipeline ID:", pipeline_id)
print("Pipeline URL:", data["web_url"])
输出：

Pipeline ID: 456789
Pipeline URL: https://gitlab.com/xxx/project/-/pipelines/456789
这个就是 pipeline 页面地址。
2 等待 pipeline 运行完成
通常要轮询：
Python
import time

status_url = f"{GITLAB_URL}/api/v4/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/pipelines/{pipeline_id}"

while True:

    res = requests.get(status_url, headers=headers)

    status = res.json()["status"]

    print("status:", status)

    if status in ["success", "failed", "canceled"]:
        break

    time.sleep(10)
3 获取 job 列表
有些 URL 在 job 里：

GET /projects/:id/pipelines/:pipeline_id/jobs
代码：
Python
jobs_url = f"{GITLAB_URL}/api/v4/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/pipelines/{pipeline_id}/jobs"

jobs = requests.get(jobs_url, headers=headers).json()

for job in jobs:
    print(job["name"], job["web_url"])
输出：

deploy https://gitlab.com/.../jobs/111
test https://gitlab.com/.../jobs/112
4 获取 job log（如果 URL 在 log 里）
Python
job_id = jobs[0]["id"]

log_url = f"{GITLAB_URL}/api/v4/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/jobs/{job_id}/trace"

log = requests.get(log_url, headers=headers).text

print(log)
然后解析：
Python
import re

url = re.search(r'https://[^\s]+', log)

if url:
    print("Found URL:", url.group())
5 如果 pipeline 使用 environment（推荐）
很多 CI/CD 会生成 environment URL：
API：

GET /projects/:id/environments
代码：
Python
env_url = f"{GITLAB_URL}/api/v4/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/environments"

envs = requests.get(env_url, headers=headers).json()

for env in envs:
    print(env["name"], env["external_url"])
输出：

review/test-123 https://test-env-123.example.com
